   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Spasines and Apollophanes to Dionusios and Asklepiades, greeting. Whereas Kastor son of Apollonios of the Ammonian deme, hipparches in command of men of the first hipparchy of the 80-arouras holders, has ceded out of the remainder of his holding at Kerkesis in the division of Polemon 6 1/2 arouras to Akousilaos son of Maron, Macedonian ï¿½ , we write to you in order that you may be careful to manage the other formalities, as is fitting. Good-bye. The [.]1st year, Epeiph [..].</ab>
         </div>
